    "This advancement will drive ITS toward greater safety and efficiency.",
    "In the field of ITS, prediction and decision-making technologies serve as another essential application.",
    "The core of these technologies lies in the comprehensive collection and in-depth analysis of various types of traffic-related data, including historical data and real-time data.",
    "On one hand, this method can assist drivers with tasks using intelligent road facilities and generative AI, promptly identify and warn of dangerous driving behaviors, and ensure driving safety.",
